Package: Rlinkedin
Version: 0.1
Title: Access to the LinkedIn API via R
Description: This package provides a series of 
  functions that allow users to access the LinkedIn API
  to get information about connections, search for
  people and jobs, share updates with their
  network, and create group discussions.
Author: Michael Piccirilli <michael.r.piccirilli@gmail.com>
Maintainer: Michael Piccirilli <michael.r.piccirilli@gmail.com>
Depends: 
    R (>= 2.12.0),
    httr,
    XML,
    httpuv    
License: GPL-2
LazyData: true
URL: https://github.com/mpiccirilli/Rlinkedin
